1. *Vodili* smo psa u park. (We were walking the dog in the park.)
2. Oni su *vodili* ljubavno pismo godinama. (They have been exchanging love letters for years.)
3. Kada smo bili mali, mama i tata su nas *vodili* na izlete. (When we were little, mom and dad used to take us on outings.)
4. Policajci su *vodili* lopova u zatvor. (The police were taking the thief to jail.)
5. Oni su *vodili* sastanak juče. (They were leading the meeting yesterday.)
6. *Vodili* smo debatu o klimatskim promenama. (We had a debate on climate change.)
7. Nije dobro da se *vodite* mišlju da ste najbolji. (It's not good to be guided by the thought that you're the best.)
8. Kada *vodimo* posao, moramo biti profesionalni. (When we run a business, we need to be professional.)
9. Da bi uspeli u životu, moramo *voditi* računa o svom zdravlju. (To succeed in life, we need to take care of our health.)
10. Oni će *voditi* ovu kompaniju u narednom periodu. (They will be leading this company in the future.)